construction, transfections and luciferase assay. Z.L. collected the 
blood samples from patients with AD and did the 18F-AV45 PET/MD 
scans. M.L., B.H., Yifan Z. and Y.W. performed the genotyping and 
behavioral tests. Yun Z. and W.S. supervised the project, analyzed all 
the data and wrote the paper. Yun Z., H.C. and Y.F. are designated as 
co-first authors due to their substantial contributions to conducting 
experiments and analyzing data. Yun Z. is listed first for her input to the 
conception of the study and her contributions to writing the paper.  
